title: Kim Vuga from SBS' 'Go Back To Where You Came' From in Senate tilt
text:
Topix › Pacific Travel › Kim Vuga from SBS' 'Go Back To Where ... Kim Vuga from SBS' 'Go Back To Where You Came' From in Senate tilt Next Story Prev Story 5 hrs ago Read more: The Age 
Kim Vuga, the Townsville resident who stars in the controversial SBS documentary Go Back To Where You Came From, appears not to have changed from her hard-line anti-refugee stance. EXCLUSIVE Kim Vuga, the Townsville grandmother who rose to prominence expressimg hardline anti-immigration and anti-Islam views on the SBS reality show Go Back To Where You Came From , will run for the Senate at the next federal election.
